    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the platform. The suspension maintains its signature handling characteristics with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing excellent lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust and the throttle response is telepathic. A true driver's specification for those who value mechanical purity.",
