      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A4 Premium Plus in Mythos Black Metallic with a refined Rock Gray leather interior. This Quattro all-wheel-drive sedan has been a reliable daily driver, balancing performance with executive comfort. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and pristine, featuring the Audi Virtual Cockpit, a panoramic sunroof, and heated seats that show only the slightest softening of the leather bolsters. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; all scheduled services were performed at the dealership, and a fresh oil change was completed last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes are responsive with no pulsation. This is a turnkey luxury sedan for a buyer who appreciates a well-documented history and a car that has been treated with respect.",
